REV Robotics

MAXPlanetary Input Couplers

REV Robotics designs, builds and manufactures robotics parts and components used by students for learning about science, technology, engineering, and math (STEM). Our parts are commonly used within the FIRST Robotics Competition and the FIRST Tech...

Price: USD 8

Note that there is a Kraken input on the list–but not quite available yet. Second item on Stock Updates says it should be available quite soon… and I’ll refer you to the REV thread (and suggest you sign up for the emails, those things will FLY out the door!) for further details on timing.
